      =\frac{2(0.082057\;\text{L·atm·K}^{-1}\text{mol}^{-1})(298.15\ \text{K})}{10\ \text{atm}}
      \approx 4.89\ \text{L}
\]

---

**2. Final volume**

Cross‑sectional area \(A = 10.0\ \text{cm}^2 = 1.0\times10^{-3}\ \text{m}^2\)

Piston displacement \(\Delta x = 20\ \text{cm}=0.20\ \text{m}\)

\[
